entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You've spoken with the Disgruntled Townspeople and Phor Cl-lan, now do what you can to bring water to the people.
entries.journal_entry_description: Find out what has Nym's people so upset and help them if you can.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Go out to where the Disgruntled Townspeople are gathered and speak with their leader.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Speak with the speaker for the Disgruntled Townspeople
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Locate Phor Cl-lan, Nym's Water Treatment Technician and speak with him about the water quality.
